Interface PolicyRule

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HasInner<ManagementPolicyRule>

    @Beta
public interface PolicyRule
extends HasInner<ManagementPolicyRule>
    An immutable client-side representation of a rule in an Azure Management Policy.
